column2: I am signing because I support Johnny Depp. There is so much evidence available that proves Amber Heard had an agenda since day one with Johnny. To hook him, take advantage of her marriage status to him as a tool to advance her career and then destroy him personally and financially with pathological lies and faked pictures. The evidence is overwhelming, and there’s so much more out there that hasn’t been tapped yet. She emotionally and physically abused Johnny throughout their marriage, leaving him having to fight for his sanity and career. And to see Disney and Warner Brothers turn their back on a man that’s made them millions hand over fist. While they side with an untalented, no body actress because she is a woman. Hollywood has know Johnny, his acting talent, box office appeal, and his personal character and work ethic. They know how highly respected he is professionally and personally. They turned their backs on him, not even listening to his side. Now they’re all regretting their decisions because the truth has come out, and it’s gonna cost them millions and the respect of the people.  Johnny has been through enough pain. It’s time he gets justice, and Amber gets a jail cell. So I will not watch Aquaman 2, along with about 200 friends and family. We boycott because our voices were not listened too regarding Ambers participation in the film. And myself and the same family and friends have stopped buying any products by L’Oréal and any of the companies that are affiliated with them. They all could have stepped up and fired her, yet even with all the proof of her deceptions and lies, they stay loyal. They’ve made a stupid and costly mistake over a pretty face with definite mental health and criminal issues.

column2: She’s a habitual domestic abuser and a bed-pooping bandit. (Who does that!?) And so transparent. So desperate to “not be just pretty but smart, too!” that she brings a hardcover library onto the set of Aquaman? (Reading books on your iphone or tablet isn’t impressive enough.) No doubt they were only the most cerebral titles/authors, too. Excuse me while I puke. She’s a frickin high school drop out. Then bragging to media outlets that married father Momoa (only the hottest man alive) is SO desperate for her attention that he ripped up her books. She has actually said, “It’s not creatively fulfilling to just be sexy. I did nothing to look the way I look. The genetic cards that anyone is dealt are not in their control, so to take pride in my looks would be a mistake.” She did “nothing” except get a nose job and her teeth fixed! But way to humble brag about being hot. What a lying fool. God, I can’t wait til her 15 minutes is over.

This is a huge double standard and an insult to Johnny Depp and mens rights. As we all know if the roles were reversed it would be a completely different outcome! (Considering his role as Jack Sparrow was ripped from him due to her accusations) Sign this petition to show your support for mens rights and Johnny Depp and demand justice!
